data.title: The Bronze Buckaroo (1939)
data.meta_description: Cowboy Bob Blake receives a letter from his friend Joe Jackson, asking for help. Blake and his men travel to Jackson’s ranch, only to discover from Jackson’s sister Betty that Joe has been missing for three weeks.
